  "title": "Sales Operation Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview</strong></p><p>Established in 2007, Piccolo Pte Ltd, operating as Piccolo House, is a Singapore-based company specializing in retail sales of children’s furniture, decorations, accessories, and mattresses. We provide high-quality kids’ furniture to help parents create the perfect dreamland for their children.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will provide sales and customer service support by assisting customers with product selections, preparing sales documents, and maintaining follow-up communication to ensure customer satisfaction.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Explain product features and benefits to customers to support informed purchasing decisions.</li><li>Respond promptly to customer inquiries to provide accurate information and assistance.</li><li>Recommend merchandise options tailored to customers’ needs and preferences.</li><li>Prepare accurate quotations, sales orders, delivery orders, and invoices to facilitate smooth sales transactions.</li><li>Follow up with customers to confirm orders and address any post-sale concerns.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirement</strong></p><ul><li>Cheerful personality and passionate about kids room interior .</li><li>Willing to work on weekends and public holidays to support business operations. </li><li>Working hours: 10am to 7pm. </li><li>Location: Ubi Techpark. </li></ul><p><strong>Job Highlights:</strong></p><ul><li>Location: Ubi Techpark, within walking distance to MRT.</li><li>Benefits include annual leave, medical benefits, AWS, and extra remuneration upon meeting sales quota.</li><li>Positive working environment</li><li>Job training will be provided. </li></ul>",
